t_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "書", "row": 3, "col": 44, "end_col": 45, "font_size": 13.0, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "(控)", "row": 3, "col": 46, "end_col": 48, "font_size": 13.0, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "日付(西暦)", "row": 3, "col": 66, "end_col": 69, "font_size": 7.2, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "グリーン産業株式会社", "row": 4, "col": 10, "end_col": 20, "font_size": 10.1, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "御中", "row": 4, "col": 21, "end_col": 23, "font_size": 10.1, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "下記のとおり請求致します。", "row": 5, "col": 10, "end_col": 20, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "取引先コード", "row": 5, "col": 55, "end_col": 60, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "（必ずご記入ください）", "row": 5, "col": 60, "end_col": 68, "font_color": "FF0000", "font_size": 7.2, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "※請求書ご提出にあたってのお願い", "row": 9, "col": 10, "end_col": 23, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "１．記入項目について", "row": 10, "col": 10, "end_col": 18, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "注文書が発行されている場合", "row": 10, "col": 14, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "・・・", "row": 10, "col": 25, "end_col": 28, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "太枠内と灰色の部分", "row": 10, "col": 28, "end_col": 35, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "注文書が発行されていない場合・・・", "row": 11, "col": 14, "end_col": 28, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "太枠内のみ", "row": 11, "col": 28, "end_col": 32, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "２．納入品目を記入しきれない場合は、総額を記入し御社の請求明細書を添付してください。", "row": 12, "col": 10, "end_col": 43, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "３．軽油税、産廃税については、「工事名（品名）」欄に個別に明記してください。", "row": 13, "col": 10, "end_col": 40, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "※提出部数", "row": 27, "col": 10, "end_col": 14, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "1部（白黒で構いません）・・・毎月５日必着", "row": 27, "col": 15, "end_col": 33, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "※毎年１２月のみ２０日締切（２５日必着）翌月末日支払いとさせていただきます。", "row": 28, "col": 10, "end_col": 43, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "〒", "row": 6, "col": 56, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 11.5, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "－", "row": 6, "col": 64, "end_col": 65, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "住", "row": 7, "col": 54, "end_col": 55, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "所", "row": 7, "col": 59, "end_col": 60, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "取引先名", "row": 8, "col": 54, "end_col": 60, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "代表者名", "row": 9, "col": 54, "end_col": 60, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "印", "row": 9, "col": 74, "end_col": 75, "font_size": 6.5, "font_name": "MS-PGothic"}, {"type": "text", "content": "電話FAX", "row": 10, "col": 60, "end_col": 62, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "－－", "row": 10, "col": 66, "end_col": 67, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "－－", "row": 10, "col": 70, "end_col": 71, "font_size": 7.9, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "登録番号Ｔ", "row": 11, "col": 54, "end_col": 62, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mincho"}, {"type": "text", "content": "振込先情報口座名義(ｶﾀｶﾅ)：銀行預金", "row": 12, "col": 54, "end_col": 65, "font_size": 8.6, "font_name": "MS-Mi